data.title: Doo Wop Shoo Bop Teen Sound CDs by Title
data.meta_description:
Doo Wop Shoo Bop various artist cd page. Each entry includes 
cd title, track listing and brief description.
data.text:
TEEN BATTLE ROYALE - Dean Christie vs Ritchie Cordell

Two teen idols battle it out - one from New York - Ritchie Cordell and the other from Pennsylvannia - Dean Christie. You get to pick the winner! 29 tracks.

TEENAGE CRUSH - Volume 3

Clean-cut teen dreams from the golden age of American Rock & Roll. Features tracks by Terry Stafford, Gino & Gina, Echoes, Innocents and many others. 28 tracks.

TEENAGE CRUSH - Volume 5

28 great teen hits taken from Billboard's Hot 100 chart during the Golden Age of Rock'n'Roll, including many rarities available on CD for the first time, together with a fabulous, picture-packed booklet telling the stories behind the sounds. 28 tracks.

TEEN-AGE DREAMS - Volume 1

Fantastic highschool rarities from the late fifties & sixties. Includes tracks by Vinnie Monte, Bobby Gee and Celestials, Class Mates, Dick Webb and many more. 33 tracks.
